With a try/except in read_max_power_file() I got s-tui working:

With -1
```
    def read_max_power_file(self):
        if not self.is_available:
            return -1
        try:
            return float(self.read_measurement(self.intel_rapl_package_max_energy_file))
        except:
            return -1
```
