Hi @afzal273!

When your search contains a dash surrounded by spaces, the filter thinks you want a range. To have the filter ignore the range search for a column, use the [`filter_excludeFilter` option](http://mottie.github.io/tablesorter/docs/#widget-filter-exclude-filter) to disable the "range" type of filters for that column ([demo](http://jsfiddle.net/Mottie/wty134u7/3/)):

```js
$('table').tablesorter({
  theme: 'blue',
  widgets: ['zebra', 'filter'],
  widgetOptions: {
    filter_excludeFilter: {
      0: 'range'
    }
  }
});
```

